race.comment: ALL IN KNOTS (2) has not raced since scoring (29.20) over 488m at this track 11 weeks ago. Solid record here winning two races. On top here on best form and expected to feature. ERIN GO BRAGH (1) has missed the frame the last couple but was a Novice race winner three back (22.55) at Cannington over 381m. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. LOCHINVAR LORD (8) had been going along well and was strongly fancied last time but could only manage fourth (23.19) at this track. One of the better hopes. GO GETTEM BERYL (7) is last start winner who looks one of the chances.
